1. add a UI by Tkinter
 + has a input at the top, a description area after it, a history list at left side
 + can toggle by Ctrl+Alt+T
 + when showing, auto focus on input
 + when hidding, clean input value
 + when press 'enter'
	+ if input is empty, auto play sound of last result
	+ if has input:
	  + if is same as last result, play sound of last result
	  + if not, translate it and play its sound, push in history list
 + can click on history list to see result of then